PLPlace.description: Serving Princeton University\'s students, faculty and staff, the Digital Print Center is the University\'s on-campus location of Print & Mail Services for all your printing and direct mail needs. We offer on-demand printing, large format output, production art services, an offset & specialty print outsource program, bindery, and lamination. Additional services include direct mail services, electronic envelope addressing, mail list processing, mail panel design review. We also provide wifi, a computer cluster, and self-serve black and white copying.
